<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="light" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sendu - Compartir Archivos</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/icons/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="icon" href="/assets/icons/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/icons/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="mask-icon" href="/assets/icons/favicon.svg" color="#dc2626">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/dist/tailwind.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest/dist/umd/lucide.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --app-background: radial-gradient(circle at 15% 15%, rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.28), transparent 45%),
                               radial-gradient(circle at 85% 20%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25), transparent 55%),
                               radial-gradient(circle at 12% 85%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18), transparent 55%),
                               linear-gradient(145deg, #050b14 0%, #101b34 100%);
            --text-color: #f8fafc;
            --muted-color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.78);
            --card-bg: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.68);
            --card-border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.28);
            --accent: #dc2626;
            --accent-strong: #ef4444;
            --shadow-soft: 0 28px 60px -32px rgba(8, 15, 35, 0.75);
        }

        html[data-theme="light"] {
            --app-background: radial-gradient(circle at 15% 15%, rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.18), transparent 45%),
                               radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18), transparent 55%),
                               linear-gradient(145deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #e7ecf4 100%);
            --text-color: #0f172a;
            --muted-color: rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.78);
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
            --card-border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
            --shadow-soft: 0 22px 50px -28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--app-background);
            color: var(--text-color);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .text-muted {
            color: var(--muted-color);
        }

        .gradient-background {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .gradient-background::before,
        .gradient-background::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -35%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.6;
            filter: blur(140px);
        }

        .gradient-background::before {
            background: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.55);
            animation: gradientPulse 14s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .gradient-background::after {
            background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5), transparent 55%, rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.4));
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
            animation: gradientRotate 22s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gradientPulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.55; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.15); opacity: 0.85; }
        }

        @keyframes gradientRotate {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1); }
        }

        .glass-panel {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            border-radius: 999px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: inherit;
        }

        .icon {
            width: 1.1rem;
            height: 1.1rem;
            stroke-width: 1.75px;
        }
        .app-nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 1.5rem;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 1100px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
            z-index: 50;
        }

        .icon-button,
        .avatar-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: inherit;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .icon-button:hover,
        .avatar-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 26px -18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
        }

        .user-menu {
            position: relative;
        }

        .user-dropdown {
            position: absolute;
            top: calc(100% + 0.75rem);
            right: 0;
            min-width: 200px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            padding: 0.6rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            z-index: 40;
        }

        .user-dropdown.show {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .user-dropdown-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            padding: 0.55rem 0.65rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            color: inherit;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .user-dropdown-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .notification {
            position: fixed;
            top: 1.5rem;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 60;
        }

        .notification-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.4rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            text-align: center;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .app-main {
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 140px 1.5rem 80px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .app-main > section {
            width: min(1100px, 100%);
        }

        .primary-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.45rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.6rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 32px -22px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.55);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
        }

        .primary-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 48px -22px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.65);
        }

        .secondary-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.45rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: inherit;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .secondary-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .link-button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .link-button:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .form-field {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.45rem;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--muted-color);
        }

        .form-control {
            padding: 0.75rem 0.85rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: inherit;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.25);
        }

        html[data-theme="light"] .form-control {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        }

        .upload-layout {
            display: grid;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .upload-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        #drop-zone {
            position: relative;
            border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
            border-radius: 22px;
            padding: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease;
        }

        #drop-zone:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.55);
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
        }

        html[data-theme="light"] #drop-zone {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.35);
        }

        #drop-zone input[type="file"] {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            opacity: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        #drop-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: inherit;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.55), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.55));
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .button-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .upload-options {
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            border: 1px dashed var(--card-border);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            padding: 1.35rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .option-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .option-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }
        }

        .success-card {
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.14);
            padding: 1.25rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        html[data-theme="light"] .success-card {
            background: rgba(187, 247, 208, 0.65);
        }

        .success-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.85rem;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        }

        .progress-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .progress-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        progress {
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border: none;
        }

        progress::-webkit-progress-bar {
            background: transparent;
        }

        progress::-webkit-progress-value {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
        }

        progress::-moz-progress-bar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
        }

        .result-link {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .copy-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.45rem;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 34px -22px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.6);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .copy-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 42px -22px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.68);
        }

        .file-panel {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .file-card {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        }

        .file-meta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .file-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        .file-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
        }

        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            color: var(--muted-color);
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }
        }

        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.62);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            z-index: 80;
        }

        .modal-card {
            width: min(420px, 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .modal-actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .wide-input {
            min-width: 220px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .app-main {
                padding: 120px 1rem 70px;
            }

            .glass-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="gradient-background" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div id="global-notification" class="notification hidden">
        <div id="global-notification-content" class="notification-card"></div>
    </div>

    <nav class="app-nav glass-panel">
        <a id="home-link" href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full text-white" style="background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.82);">S</span>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">Sendu</span>
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <button type="button" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Cambiar tema" class="icon-button">
                <i data-lucide="sun" class="icon"></i>
            </button>
            <div class="user-menu">
                <button type="button" id="user-menu-btn" class="avatar-button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                    <i data-lucide="user" class="icon"></i>
                </button>
                <div id="user-dropdown" class="user-dropdown"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main id="app-container" class="app-main"></main>
    <template id="upload-view-template">
        <section class="space-y-10">
            <div class="text-center space-y-3">
                <span class="badge justify-center mx-auto">
                    <i data-lucide="sparkles" class="icon"></i>
                    Transferencias seguras
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold">Comparte archivos en segundos</h1>
                <p class="text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Sube archivos grandes, añade una contraseña opcional y comparte un enlace listo para usar.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="upload-layout">
                <form id="upload-form" class="glass-card space-y-8">
                    <label for="file-input" id="drop-zone">
                        <i data-lucide="upload-cloud" class="icon" style="width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem;"></i>
                        <span id="drop-main-text" class="text-lg font-semibold">Arrastra tu archivo aquí</span>
                        <span id="drop-sub-text" class="text-muted">o haz clic para seleccionar</span>
                        <span class="badge">Tamaño máximo 10GB</span>
                        <input type="file" id="file-input" class="file-input">
                        <div id="drop-overlay">
                            <i data-lucide="download" class="icon" style="width: 2rem; height: 2rem;"></i>
                            <div>Suelta el archivo para subir</div>
                        </div>
                    </label>

                    <div class="button-row">
                        <button type="button" id="start-upload" class="primary-btn">
                            <i data-lucide="send" class="icon"></i>
                            Iniciar subida
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" id="clear-selection" class="secondary-btn opacity-50 pointer-events-none" disabled>
                            <i data-lucide="rotate-ccw" class="icon"></i>
                            Limpiar selección
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div id="upload-options" class="upload-options hidden">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold">Opciones avanzadas</h3>
                        <div class="option-grid">
                            <label class="form-field">
                                <span class="form-label">Contraseña (opcional)</span>
                                <input type="password" id="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Dejar vacío para sin contraseña" autocomplete="new-password">
                            </label>
                            <label class="form-field">
                                <span class="form-label">Expiración (días)</span>
                                <input type="number" id="expires" class="form-control" placeholder="0 = Sin expiración" min="0" max="15" inputmode="numeric">
                            </label>
                            <label class="form-field">
                                <span class="form-label">Descargas máximas</span>
                                <input type="number" id="maxDownloads" class="form-control" placeholder="Vacío = ilimitado" min="1">
                                <span class="text-muted text-sm">Define cuántas descargas se permiten antes de que el enlace caduque.</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="upload-success-banner" class="success-card hidden">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Archivo listo para compartir</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted text-sm">Copia el enlace generado y compártelo con quien quieras.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="success-grid">
                            <input type="text" id="upload-success-url" readonly class="form-control flex-1 wide-input" name="download-url">
                            <button type="button" id="upload-success-copy" class="copy-button">
                                <i data-lucide="copy" class="icon"></i>
                                Copiar enlace
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="upload-list" class="progress-list"></div>
                </form>

                <aside class="glass-card space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Consejos rápidos</h3>
                    <ul class="info-list">
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="icon"></i>
                            Protege tus enlaces con contraseña para mayor seguridad.
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <i data-lucide="clock" class="icon"></i>
                            Define una expiración para controlar el acceso temporal.
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <i data-lucide="sparkles" class="icon"></i>
                            Gestiona tus archivos desde el panel en cualquier momento.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </section>
    </template>

    <template id="download-view-template">
        <section class="space-y-8">
            <div class="glass-card space-y-6 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <span class="badge justify-center mx-auto">
                        <i data-lucide="download" class="icon"></i>
                        Descarga disponible
                    </span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Tu archivo está preparado</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted">Introduce la contraseña si es necesaria y descárgalo al instante.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="glass-card space-y-2">
                    <p id="file-name" class="file-name text-lg">nombre_archivo.zip</p>
                    <p id="file-size" class="text-muted text-sm">0 MB</p>
                </div>

                <form id="download-form" class="space-y-4 max-w-md mx-auto text-left">
                    <div id="password-group" class="form-field hidden">
                        <span class="form-label">Contraseña</span>
                        <input type="password" id="download-password" class="form-control" placeholder="••••••••">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" id="download-button" class="primary-btn w-full justify-center">
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-down-circle" class="icon"></i>
                        Descargar archivo
                    </button>
                </form>

                <p id="expiry-info" class="text-muted text-sm hidden"></p>
                <div id="download-error-message" class="error-banner hidden"></div>
